
{{alias}}( z )

    infinity.

    Parameters
    ----------
    z: Complex128
        Complex number.

    Returns
    -------
    out: Complex128
        Result.

    > var v = {{alias}}( new {{alias:@stdlib/complex/float64/ctor}}( 5.5, 3.3 ) )
    <Complex128>
    > var re = {{alias:@stdlib/complex/real}}( v )
    5.0
    > var im = {{alias:@stdlib/complex/imag}}( v )
